Class ShapeMenuViewController

java.lang.Object
View.ShapeMenu.ShapeMenuViewController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ShapeMenuViewController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Controller of the menu to add a new shape. It is linked to the "AddShapeMenuController.fxml" file It handles the behavior of the pop-up window
